Subject: Re: 2.6.8-rc1 and before: IO-APIC + DRI + RTL8139 = Disabling Ethernet IRQ
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
